      "text": "Fifi the Fox lived in a sunny forest. She had bright orange fur and a wagging tail. Fifi loved to explore, but sometimes she felt shy around new friends.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2Fe99b9ac7-1cfa-4f91-bcfa-39f3e31ed602_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775929241&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=LUqN9MR8Gqh0PjPznpVZuvEp68w%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "One day, Milo the Mouse and Dottle the Duck came by. 'Hi, Fifi! Will you play with us?' they asked. Fifi hesitated, but she liked their smiles.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2F339d4e5a-c8f6-4ae6-94f5-5dcad85b0b2b_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775929265&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=8%2Bk9D%2BHbxFHGaTDmJzCgf9HhFI0%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "Fifi suggested a game of hide-and-seek. She hid behind a big tree, waiting for the others. But when they couldn't find her, she felt lonely.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2F9da8ef88-781c-48f5-9bf1-d0747ecf1ffe_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775929303&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=xzlD%2FbaGvne6trHnVmfXh3DgZ4Q%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "Milo and Dottle finally found Fifi. 'Why are you sad?' they asked. Fifi realized she wanted to play together, not alone. She felt happy again.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2F3d7f4212-d136-437d-a866-fd7692191cd0_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775929333&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=sIU9dO9x89Am6RyJcSvarC3TEDk%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "The three friends laughed and chased each other through the meadow. They shared treats and told silly jokes. Fifi learned that playing with friends is more fun.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2F58527821-0c34-4629-b393-677d92c35042_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775929352&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=nzMvD2emGyNb3RPB7qCOFKr8HO4%3D",
      "audio": null,
      "video": null
    },
    {
      "text": "As the sun set, Fifi hugged Milo and Dottle. 'Thank you for being my friends,' she said. They all smiled, knowing they would always be together.",
      "image": "http://hailuo-image-algeng-data-us.oss-us-east-1.aliyuncs.com/image_inference_output%2Ftalkie%2Fprod%2Fimg%2F2026-04-11%2F96e307e9-7a02-4254-b8f2-fa9eade48d30_aigc.jpeg?Expires=1775929375&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tRDTcyEYLLuBEpJRwCi&Signature=bT5j2FAIoDv9sO21O%2BN%2BHVOs5Vw%3D",
